        <div class="content-body">
          <p>Studying abroad is an exciting opportunity, but it requires careful planning to get right. At Grant Consulting, we help students in Tashkent and across Uzbekistan build a clear academic roadmap — from selecting the right program and intake season to preparing all requirements well in advance. A well-structured plan turns what can feel overwhelming into a manageable, step-by-step process.</p>
          <p>Timing is everything when it comes to international applications. We create personalized timelines that account for language test preparation, document collection, application deadlines, and visa processing windows. By mapping out every milestone months ahead, we ensure nothing is rushed and nothing is missed.</p>
          <p>Understanding the financial side of studying abroad is just as important as the academic side. We provide transparent budget guidance covering tuition fees, living costs, insurance, and travel expenses for each destination. Our consultants also identify funding options — including scholarships, grants, and part-time work allowances — so students and their families can plan with confidence.</p>
        </div>

